==French==

===Verb===
'''acheter'''

# To [[purchase]]; to [[buy]]

====Usage Note====
In the [[je]], [[tu]], [[il]], and [[ils]] [[conjugation]]s, the first e becomes è (e with an accent grave) (i.e., ''j'achète'', tu ''achètes'', il ''achète'', ils ''achètent'').

